 ono sridon,

614
00:33:55,900 --> 00:33:56,740
 u 8 sati,

615
00:33:56,740 --> 00:33:58,380
 najvećer imam balun sa kipom.

616
00:33:58,380 --> 00:33:59,620
 20 zadnjih godina,

617
00:33:59,620 --> 00:34:00,740
 nije to sad nešto.

618
00:34:00,740 --> 00:34:03,580
 I onda bi ja nekad primijetio

619
00:34:03,580 --> 00:34:05,680
 da se ona,

620
00:34:05,680 --> 00:34:07,720
 da je ljubomorna.

621
00:34:09,060 --> 00:34:10,220
 ona je rodila,

622
00:34:10,220 --> 00:34:11,340
 doji,

623
00:34:11,340 --> 00:34:13,120
 invalid je za sport,

624
00:34:13,120 --> 00:34:13,800
 znači,

625
00:34:13,800 --> 00:34:14,300
 ne može,

626
00:34:14,300 --> 00:34:15,580
 ničim se ne može baviti,

627
00:34:15,580 --> 00:34:16,620
 nego samo mora dojti.

628
00:34:16,620 --> 00:34:18,940
 I teško joj je.

629
00:34:18,940 --> 00:34:20,840
 Možda ja to u tom trenutku

630
00:34:20,840 --> 00:34:22,600
 nisam dovoljno razumija

631
00:34:22,600 --> 00:34:23,840
 i možda nisam bila nekako

632
00:34:23,840 --> 00:34:24,820
 dovoljna podrška,

633
00:34:24,820 --> 00:34:25,120
 ne znam,

634
00:34:25,120 --> 00:34:25,840
 sa razgovorom,

635
00:34:25,900 --> 00:34:26,500
 s ovim sonim.

636
00:34:26,500 --> 00:34:27,480
 Međutim,

637
00:34:27,480 --> 00:34:28,400
 ja nisam rodija,

638
00:34:28,400 --> 00:34:30,120
 ja nisam doija

639
00:34:30,120 --> 00:34:33,960
 i ja i dalje imam sridon u 8 sati,

640
00:34:33,960 --> 00:34:34,740
 najvećer balun.

641
00:34:34,740 --> 00:34:38,200
 I onda bi ona nekad

642
00:34:38,200 --> 00:34:40,380
 znala meni zažugat,

643
00:34:40,380 --> 00:34:41,340
 kako to,

644
00:34:41,340 --> 00:34:42,160
 ono,

645
00:34:42,160 --> 00:34:43,520
 možda ne bi ni žugala,

646
00:34:43,520 --> 00:34:44,680
 ali bi ja to primijetio,

647
00:34:44,680 --> 00:34:45,600
 da njoj smeta,

648
00:34:45,600 --> 00:34:47,300
 što ja ide na balun u 8 uri,

649
00:34:47,300 --> 00:34:47,620
 ne znam,

650
00:34:47,620 --> 00:34:48,180
 sridon.

651
00:34:48,180 --> 00:34:50,220
 Njoj to smeta.

652
00:34:50,220 --> 00:34:53,200
 A meni je to smetalo

653
00:34:53,200 --> 00:34:54,060
 što njoj smeta.

654
00:34:54,060 --> 00:34:57,580
 I ja sam njoj tvrdija tada,

655
00:34:57,580 --> 00:34:59,440
 jer ja sam,

656
00:34:59,440 --> 00:34:59,800
 znači,

657
00:34:59,800 --> 00:35:00,800
 takav muž,

658
00:35:00,800 --> 00:35:01,260
 znači,

659
00:35:01,260 --> 00:35:03,860
 neman ja balun svaku večer

660
00:35:03,860 --> 00:35:05,280
 idem čao od svoje žene

661
00:35:05,280 --> 00:35:06,600
 koje ove doma teško.

662
00:35:06,600 --> 00:35:07,040
 Znači,

663
00:35:07,040 --> 00:35:08,560
 doma sam prisutan,

664
00:35:08,560 --> 00:35:11,620
 volimo zajedno provoditi vrijeme,

665
00:35:11,620 --> 00:35:12,820
 idemo u šetnje,

666
00:35:12,820 --> 00:35:14,520
 kuvanjoj, pomažen,

667
00:35:14,520 --> 00:35:15,620
 ono, znači,

668
00:35:15,620 --> 00:35:16,940
 ispunjavam svoje

669
00:35:16,940 --> 00:35:19,180
 staleške dužnosti,

670
00:35:19,180 --> 00:35:19,440
 znači,

671
00:35:19,440 --> 00:35:21,300
 stvarno sam prisutan u obitelji

672
00:35:21,300 --> 00:35:23,600
 i ta obitelj mi je u stvari centar,

673
00:35:23,600 --> 00:35:25,920
 amo reći tu na zemlji,

674
00:35:25,920 --> 00:35:26,280
 ono,

675
00:35:26,280 --> 00:35:27,480
 nekako,

676
00:35:27,480 --> 00:35:28,460
 od čega se vrtim,

677
00:35:28,460 --> 00:35:29,260
 za koga brinem,

678
00:35:29,260 --> 00:35:29,420
 ja?

679
00:35:29,420 --> 00:35:32,620
 I onda ja ide na baluni,

680
00:35:32,620 --> 00:35:32,920
 vidim,

681
00:35:32,920 --> 00:35:34,600
 ona je ljubomorna

682
00:35:34,600 --> 00:35:36,480
 ili njoj to za smeta.

683
00:35:36,480 --> 00:35:37,180
 Pa ja kažem,

684
00:35:37,180 --> 00:35:38,320
 zašto ti to smeta?

685
00:35:38,320 --> 00:35:38,800
 Pa onda,

686
00:35:38,800 --> 00:35:40,180
 onda ona kaže,

687
00:35:40,180 --> 00:35:41,000
 a ja ne mogu,

688
00:35:41,000 --> 00:35:41,800
 a ti možeš.

689
00:35:41,800 --> 00:35:44,300
 Pa u tome jeca,

690
00:35:44,300 --> 00:35:44,640
 aka,

691
00:35:44,640 --> 00:35:46,640
 kad ti ne možeš,

692
00:35:46,940 --> 00:35:49,620
 a ja mogu da se ti raduješ zbog mene.

693
00:35:49,620 --> 00:35:50,560
 Znači,

694
00:35:50,560 --> 00:35:51,940
 to ti je ljubav prava.

695
00:35:51,940 --> 00:35:53,880
 Jer,

696
00:35:53,880 --> 00:35:57,120
 ja nema razloga da ne odem sa prijateljima na nogomet,

697
00:35:57,120 --> 00:35:58,440
 ja se idem samo igrat.

698
00:35:58,440 --> 00:35:59,340
 Znači,

699
00:35:59,340 --> 00:36:01,420
 ja sam sa svom ženom bio cijeli dan,

700
00:36:02,280 --> 00:36:03,260
 došla mi je na večer,

701
00:36:03,260 --> 00:36:04,420
 idem igra nogomet.

702
00:36:04,420 --> 00:36:06,100
 Ne radim,

703
00:36:06,100 --> 00:36:07,740
 ništa znači protiv tebe,

704
00:36:07,740 --> 00:36:08,160
 ne idem,

705
00:36:08,160 --> 00:36:09,620
 ona u svoj glavi bi,

706
00:36:09,620 --> 00:36:12,740
 ona bi nekako složila priču,

707
00:36:12,740 --> 00:36:15,360
 da ja njoj za dišpet ide na balun sa svojim prijateljima.

708
00:36:15,360 --> 00:36:18,380
 A ja se samo idem igrat sa svojim prijateljima,

709
00:36:18,380 --> 00:36:20,420
 kojih imam već 20 zadnjih godina.

710
00:36:21,420 --> 00:36:23,200
 I onda sam rekao jedan put,

711
00:36:23,200 --> 00:36:24,000
 zamisli sad,

712
00:36:24,000 --> 00:36:26,400
 ti mi imamo sina,

713
00:36:26,400 --> 00:36:28,520
 on ima 10-15 godina,

714
00:36:28,520 --> 00:36:30,460
 ima na večer u 8 balun,

715
00:36:30,460 --> 00:36:32,920
 i on dođe s nogometa,

716
00:36:32,920 --> 00:36:33,880
 i ti njega ono,

717
00:36:33,880 --> 00:36:35,400
 a kako je bilo na nogomet,

718
00:36:35,400 --> 00:36:37,700
 to će ti mama napravi palač i inke,

719
00:36:37,700 --> 00:36:41,280
 o ćeš pozva nekog prijatelja da dođe tu na čaj i to.

720
00:36:41,280 --> 00:36:44,320
 E, a takva bi bila prema sinu.

721
00:36:44,320 --> 00:36:45,200
 A ja sam ti muž,

722
00:36:45,200 --> 00:36:47,640
 mene moraš volit još više od svog sina.

723
00:36:47,640 --> 00:36:48,640
 Janjetinu.

724
00:36:48,640 --> 00:36:50,360
 E, Janjetinu hoću, brate.

725
00:36:51,420 --> 00:36:59,640
 I, stvarno, tu se upalja taj neki kliker njoj,

726
00:36:59,640 --> 00:37:01,080
 i stvarno je kasnije,

727
00:37:01,080 --> 00:37:03,440
 ne bi mi žugala,

728
00:37:03,440 --> 00:37:04,880
 nego sam primijetija,

729
00:37:04,880 --> 00:37:06,420
 sam na njoj,

730
00:37:06,420 --> 00:37:11,460
 da je reprogramirala neki čip,

731
00:37:11,460 --> 00:37:13,040
 tu unutra,

732
00:37:13,040 --> 00:37:15,580
 ima tu dosta čipova,

733
00:37:15,580 --> 00:37:18,780
 nemamo sad vrimena,

734
00:37:18,780 --> 00:37:20,580
 jer mi sad zapoure,

735
00:37:21,420 --> 00:37:27,300
 ali ona se počela stvarno radovat zbog toga šta ja mogu otići od vozi biciklu,

736
00:37:27,300 --> 00:37:29,200
 a ona ne može.

737
00:37:29,200 --> 00:37:32,640
 Znači, stvarno se radovala,

738
00:37:32,640 --> 00:37:35,840
 jer to su sve hobi koje smo mi prije zajedno radili,

739
00:37:35,840 --> 00:37:37,200
 nismo išli na balon skupa,

740
00:37:37,200 --> 00:37:41,420
 ali išli bi planinarit, išli bi penjati, išli bi vozi bicikle,

741
00:37:41,420 --> 00:37:43,720
 i ja bi i dalje tija to raditi sa njom,

742
00:37:43,720 --> 00:37:44,960
 ali jednostavno ona ne može.

743
00:37:44,960 --> 00:37:47,640
 I ja ponekad idem to raditi.

744
00:37:48,020 --> 00:37:49,720
 Znači, raduj se zbog mene,

745
00:37:49,720 --> 00:37:51,380
 ja se radujem zbog nje.

746
00:37:51,380 --> 00:37:54,240
 Znači, meni je drago kad moja žena ide,

747
00:37:54,240 --> 00:37:59,400
 evo sad ide u Lourdes sa najstarijom čeri za koliko, za 20 dana.

748
00:37:59,400 --> 00:38:01,160
 Idu sedam dana u Lourdes.

749
00:38:01,160 --> 00:38:03,820
 Pa ja sam presretan što ona može ići u Lourdes

750
00:38:03,820 --> 00:38:05,880
 i šta sam ja ostati s ovih četvoro najmlađih

751
00:38:05,880 --> 00:38:07,260
 koji će me popiti krv.

752
00:38:07,260 --> 00:38:09,620
 Sad raće me.

753
00:38:09,620 --> 00:38:12,700
 Ali ja smatram da sam ja privilegiran

754
00:38:12,700 --> 00:38:14,800
 šta mogu ostati sa četvoro,

755
00:38:14,800 --> 00:38:18,100
 uzeti godišnji odmor i čuvati svojih četvoro dice.

756
00:38:18,100 --> 00:38:19,800
 Smatram da je to privilegija.

757
00:38:19,800 --> 00:38:21,940
 Šta mogu minja pelene,

758
00:38:21,940 --> 00:38:24,580
 dok mi ovi drugi kriče i govore da su gladni.

759
00:38:24,580 --> 00:38:26,920
 Šta je stvarno privilegija.

760
00:38:26,920 --> 00:38:30,040
 Znači, danas mi živimo u nekom svijetu

761
00:38:30,040 --> 00:38:32,480
 da je samo da je meni fino, da je meni dobro,

762
00:38:32,640 --> 00:38:34,400
 pa kome je lijepše nego meni.

763
00:38:34,400 --> 00:38:38,760
 To je toliko bogatstvo da su iskrivljene,

764
00:38:38,760 --> 00:38:40,080
 ono bare je napisao,

765
00:38:40,080 --> 00:38:42,280
 iskrivljene vrijednosti,

766
00:38:42,280 --> 00:38:44,600
 da je kojim putem krenuti, ono.

767
00:38:44,600 --> 00:38:45,340
 Eto.

768
00:38:45,340 --> 00:38:47,300
 I onda ljudi pitaju,

769
00:38:47,300 --> 00:38:49,480
 pa imaš li ti šta vremena za sebe?

770
00:38:49,480 --> 00:38:50,680
 Ima, ja kažem.

771
00:38:50,680 --> 00:38:52,880
 Od 0 do 24 je svoje vrijeme za mene,

772
00:38:52,880 --> 00:38:56,320
 samo što sam ga ja odlučio pokloniti manjima od sebe.

773
00:38:56,320 --> 00:38:57,900
 I to je to.

774
00:39:02,460 --> 00:39:06,220
 Može, replika Mare,

775
00:39:06,220 --> 00:39:07,600
 imaš li što zna dodati?

776
00:39:07,600 --> 00:39:09,140
 Ma, evo, samo na ovu,

777
00:39:09,140 --> 00:39:11,180
 na taj kliker o kojem je priča.

778
00:39:11,180 --> 00:39:15,900
 To dan danas se ne zna koji je to kliker.

779
00:39:17,180 --> 00:39:18,860
 Ja sam shvatila u stvari,

780
00:39:18,860 --> 00:39:20,620
 promatrajući brakove oko sebe,

781
00:39:20,620 --> 00:39:21,940
 od starijih ljudi,

782
00:39:21,940 --> 00:39:24,240
 recimo vršnjaka mojih roditelja,

783
00:39:24,240 --> 00:39:25,180
 tako te ekipe,

784
00:39:25,180 --> 00:39:28,660
 ja sam shvatila ono da oni žive nekako dvostruke živote,

785
00:39:28,660 --> 00:39:30,240
 da svaki ima svoju televiziju,

786
00:39:30,240 --> 00:39:31,860
 ona je serija, on nogomet,

787
00:39:32,340 --> 00:39:34,320
 da svaki ima svoje društvo,

788
00:39:34,320 --> 00:39:38,300
 da svaki onako nekako živi neki svoj život unutar zajedničkog kućanstva,

789
00:39:38,300 --> 00:39:39,340
 jer djeca su već otišla.

790
00:39:40,480 --> 00:39:42,000
 i ja sam se sablaznila,

791
00:39:42,000 --> 00:39:44,620
 znači ja sam shvatila da ja ako tako nastavim,

792
00:39:44,620 --> 00:39:46,160
 da ću upravo to imat,

793
00:39:46,160 --> 00:39:47,600
 znači svak će imat svoj život,

794
00:39:47,600 --> 00:39:48,940
 on će imat svoj nogomet,

795
00:39:48,940 --> 00:39:51,200
 ja ću ne znam šta izmisliti drugo,

796
00:39:51,200 --> 00:39:55,180
 da imam i ja sam shvatila da se ja moram mijenjati

797
00:39:55,180 --> 00:39:57,100
 i koliko god to bilo teško,

798
00:39:57,100 --> 00:39:58,640
 znala sam da ima smisla,

799
00:39:58,640 --> 00:40:00,560
 jer sam tila da nakon što na dica odu,

800
00:40:00,560 --> 00:40:03,180
 da mi opet sidemo na bicikle i da se malo provozamo,

801
00:40:03,180 --> 00:40:04,900
 a ne da budemo stranci.

802
00:40:04,900 --> 00:40:09,200
 I to mi je bilo važnije nego to što se ja moram mijenjati.

803
00:40:09,200 --> 00:40:11,060
 i tu sam nekako pogazila to

804
00:40:11,060 --> 00:40:13,040
 i rekla sam, ok, sad ću se radovat,

805
00:40:13,040 --> 00:40:14,720
 i sad ću se baš radovat,

806
00:40:14,720 --> 00:40:16,680
 jer to reću, pitaću ga šta treba,

807
00:40:16,680 --> 00:40:17,800
 kako mu je bilo ono,

808
00:40:17,800 --> 00:40:19,260
 jer ja to prije stvarno nisam znala.

809
00:40:19,260 --> 00:40:22,180
 Ja to nisam jednostavno imala di vidit

810
00:40:22,180 --> 00:40:23,740
 i nisam to naučila

811
00:40:23,740 --> 00:40:27,060
 i to mi je bilo ono kao strano,

812
00:40:27,060 --> 00:40:28,680
 nisam znala da to može biti uopće.

813
00:40:28,680 --> 00:40:30,780
 Tako da smo mi kroz to,

814
00:40:30,780 --> 00:40:34,900
 nekako ja mogu reći da sam tu baš ono rasla

815
00:40:34,900 --> 00:40:37,040
 u svim tim našim, mora reći, svađama

816
00:40:37,040 --> 00:40:38,320
 i svim tim nekim stvarima

817
00:40:38,320 --> 00:40:39,200
 koje je trebalo mijenjati,

818
00:40:39,200 --> 00:40:41,980
 ono, mislim da je to bila ogroman blagoslov,

819
00:40:41,980 --> 00:40:44,320
 zato što imala sam čovjeka kre sebe

820
00:40:44,320 --> 00:40:46,740
 koji me može nešto drugačije reći,

821
00:40:46,740 --> 00:40:50,140
 kako to zapravo bi trebalo možda izgledati.

822
00:40:50,140 --> 00:40:51,280
 Isto tako i on,

823
00:40:51,280 --> 00:40:53,180
 kad bi imao neke svoje stvari,

824
00:40:53,180 --> 00:40:55,940
 ja bi isto njega upozoravala,

825
00:40:55,940 --> 00:40:58,440
 mislim, jednostavno si tu zajedno

826
00:40:58,440 --> 00:41:00,280
 i ono, živiš i rasteš.

827
00:41:00,280 --> 00:41:02,700
 Bogu hvala.

828
00:41:02,700 --> 00:41:04,480
 Imamo još vremena,

829
00:41:04,480 --> 00:41:07,720
 pa ja bih radao da neko iz publike postavi pitanje.

830
00:41:07,720 --> 00:41:09,060
 Naravno, dignite ruku

831
00:41:09,060 --> 00:41:11,680
 i dobit ćete mikrofon.

832
00:41:15,100 --> 00:41:16,560
 Evo, Saša ima pitanje.

833
00:41:16,560 --> 00:41:30,180
 E, Mio i Mare,

834
00:41:30,180 --> 00:41:31,520
 hvala vam puno na ovom sviju odnočanstvu,

835
00:41:31,520 --> 00:41:32,920
 baš ste nas ovoga i nasmijali

836
00:41:32,920 --> 00:41:33,640
 i nadahnuli.

837
00:41:34,260 --> 00:41:35,020
 Imam jedno pitanje.

838
00:41:35,020 --> 00:41:38,820
 Spomenuo si Mio da si bio u ekipi

839
00:41:38,820 --> 00:41:41,200
 u kojoj crkva se baš nije gledala onako dobro.

840
00:41:41,200 --> 00:41:43,620
 Zanima me na koliko ste vi ljudi

841
00:41:43,620 --> 00:41:45,100
 uticali iz te svoje ekipe

842
00:41:45,100 --> 00:41:46,700
 i da li su ljudi,

843
00:41:46,700 --> 00:41:48,060
 da li su mnogi,

844
00:41:48,060 --> 00:41:49,540
 ili se sami od sebe

845
00:41:49,540 --> 00:41:50,560
 ili s vremenom promijenili

846
00:41:50,560 --> 00:41:52,200
 i više počeli ići u crkvu i tako.

847
00:41:52,200 --> 00:41:54,360
 Da li ti s kojima ideš na balon,

848
00:41:54,360 --> 00:41:56,240
 da li su neki od njih sada vjernici

849
00:41:56,240 --> 00:41:58,200
 ili kako se tu događale stvari?

850
00:41:58,200 --> 00:42:01,040
 Ja to znam često ište pričati.

851
00:42:02,140 --> 00:42:04,580
 Dobro, na neke djeluješ direktno,

852
00:42:04,580 --> 00:42:05,720
 na neke indirektno,

853
00:42:05,720 --> 00:42:06,860
 na neke uopće ne,

854
00:42:06,860 --> 00:42:09,840
 ali ja se stičam kad sam se molija

855
00:42:09,840 --> 00:42:12,480
 tad kad sam živija u postanaru,

856
00:42:12,480 --> 00:42:13,340
 ima sam cimera.

857
00:42:13,340 --> 00:42:15,320
 Zajedno smo plaćali,

858
00:42:15,320 --> 00:42:17,140
 to ja, moj kolega sa faksa,

859
00:42:17,140 --> 00:42:19,580
