00:53:46,540 --> 00:53:47,220
 jedan drugoga,

1397
00:53:47,320 --> 00:53:47,960
 jednostavno,

1398
00:53:47,960 --> 00:53:48,860
 ne znam,

1399
00:53:48,860 --> 00:53:50,780
 podupiremo još na te stvari.

1400
00:53:50,780 --> 00:53:52,600
 I nije to uvijek isto,

1401
00:53:52,600 --> 00:53:53,780
 jer u periodima

1402
00:53:53,780 --> 00:53:54,420
 kad ja,

1403
00:53:54,420 --> 00:53:54,720
 ne znam,

1404
00:53:54,720 --> 00:53:55,220
 sam trudna

1405
00:53:55,220 --> 00:53:56,020
 ili taman rodin,

1406
00:53:56,020 --> 00:53:58,060
 onda nije baš zgodno,

1407
00:53:58,060 --> 00:53:58,580
 ali,

1408
00:53:58,580 --> 00:54:00,180
 to je sve u fazama,

1409
00:54:00,180 --> 00:54:01,500
 koja je ova molitva krunice,

1410
00:54:01,500 --> 00:54:01,840
 ono,

1411
00:54:01,840 --> 00:54:03,720
 nekad se moraš prilagoditi obitelj

1412
00:54:03,720 --> 00:54:05,180
 i malo staviti te stvari sa strane,

1413
00:54:05,180 --> 00:54:05,920
 ali u principu,

1414
00:54:05,920 --> 00:54:06,720
 to je tu negdje,

1415
00:54:06,720 --> 00:54:07,300
 non stop,

1416
00:54:07,300 --> 00:54:09,300
 i uvijek kad se stvori neko vrijeme,

1417
00:54:09,300 --> 00:54:10,980
 nije problem nikom od nas izaći,

1418
00:54:10,980 --> 00:54:11,620
 reći,

1419
00:54:11,620 --> 00:54:13,300
 ja bi sad baš morala izaći,

1420
00:54:13,300 --> 00:54:13,560
 malo,

1421
00:54:17,320 --> 00:54:17,580
 pet,

1422
00:54:17,580 --> 00:54:17,920
 znači,

1423
00:54:17,920 --> 00:54:18,660
 nije to baš,

1424
00:54:18,660 --> 00:54:19,360
 ali,

1425
00:54:19,360 --> 00:54:19,900
 ono,

1426
00:54:19,900 --> 00:54:21,160
 nikad nema problem s tim,

1427
00:54:21,160 --> 00:54:22,380
 da mi ono,

1428
00:54:22,380 --> 00:54:23,180
 da to vrijeme,

1429
00:54:23,180 --> 00:54:24,680
 da mogu izaći.

1430
00:54:24,680 --> 00:54:26,860
 I zadnje pitanje za Sinišu,

1431
00:54:26,860 --> 00:54:28,620
 evo pa ću vam morati lagom krenuti na misu.

1432
00:54:28,640 --> 00:54:32,400
 Evo, ja ću kratko samo pitanje za brata Miju.

1433
00:54:32,400 --> 00:54:34,500
 Što je bilo sa onim biciklom?

1434
00:54:34,500 --> 00:54:35,800
 S početka priče.

1435
00:54:35,800 --> 00:54:36,860
 Jesi ga napravio?

1436
00:54:36,860 --> 00:54:38,420
 Eno, doma je vik.

1437
00:54:38,420 --> 00:54:39,040
 E, to je.

1438
00:54:39,040 --> 00:54:40,540
 E, je li popravljena?

1439
00:54:40,540 --> 00:54:41,860
 To to je li popravljeno?

1440
00:54:41,860 --> 00:54:42,560
 Je li popravljeno?

1441
00:54:42,560 --> 00:54:44,100
 Pa, polu.

1442
00:54:44,100 --> 00:54:45,680
 A, dobro je, dobro je.

1443
00:54:45,680 --> 00:54:47,500
 A za mare utjeha,

1444
00:54:47,500 --> 00:54:52,820
 ja sam nakon 34 godine ženi za godišnicu

1445
00:54:52,820 --> 00:54:55,200
